item.title: Food Baby
item.description: Food Baby mobile app design 2021 - 1st Place Google Cloud Award @ cmd-f Why did we make this app? For the to-be-moms around the world, sometimes knowing what is healthy for their baby isn’t always clear. Although some foods and drinks like alcohol are easier to identify as harmful, there are also more obscure foods like cheese and chips that are less obvious and sometimes harmful in certain amounts.
